translation: From the Kanesh colony to ... the messenger of our messenger, so that the tablet will come to the City.
Of the tablet from the City when the City has been deposited in the City - all this Damiq has been deposited in Nemilum. Damiq will not raise claim against the colony.

Once or twice you have seized us and send me word about how much good quality go to the palace to the palace, but he does not go to the palace. Do not go to the palace. Do not go to the palace. My dear father answered the very first transport.
